item.title: CVE-2020-9519|2024-08-04T10:34:38.168Z -- micro%20focus%20international -- service%20manager%20%28server%29.
item.description: HTTP methods reveled in Web services vulnerability in Micro Focus Service manager (server), affecting versions 9.40, 9.41, 9.50, 9.51, 9.52, 9.60, 9.61, 9.62, 9.63. The vulnerability could be exploited to allow exposure of configuration data.
